high time is a 1960 american comedy film directed by blake edwards and starring bing crosby , fabian , tuesday weld , and nicole maurey . the film is told from the perspective of a middle-aged man who enters the world of a new generation of postwar youth . in the years since its release , high time has come to be viewed as a comedic study of the slowly emerging generation gap between the music and mores of an older generation and postwar youth , as well as an &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; time capsule of american adolescents and lifestyles in 1960 .